  <contentSectionDescription><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>The great outdoors - it's not just our playground, it's our inspiration. For over 85 years our purpose has always been simple, to help you get out there and join us, to explore and soak up your surroundings - one step at a time.</p>
<p>Along the way, we've learnt a lot too, and we're bursting with excitement to share our stories with you. So pack your boots and your love for the great outdoors - we'll handle the rest.</p>
<h3>Stay and Walk: Holidays With Walking</h3>
<p>No need to pack up and move every night. Pick your base from our collection of the best walking destinations across Europe and start exploring. Hike to the top for that epic view. Or simply sip on a spritz in the sunshine. With no set itineraries, you can walk as much or as little as you like. Plus, we've got your travel and accommodation sorted too.</p>
<h3>On The Ground Reps: Your Guides to Adventure</h3>
<p>Available in person, or just a phone call away, our on-the-ground Inghams team are your friendly experts to turn to for advice, whether it's about the best tried-and-tested walks, must-visit lunch spots, or local secrets. They're your go-to for making the most out of your holiday.</p>
<h3>Expert-Led Walks: Explore With The Best</h3>
<p>Ever dreamt of exploring breath-taking landscapes with an expert by your side? With us you can join up to two expert-led walks a week all included in your holiday package. These experts know the terrain like the back of their walking boots!</p>
<h3>Which Holiday Will You Step Into?</h3>
<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Experience the excitement of an Inghams walking holiday and discover the best destinations in Europe. See, explore and discover incredible cities, amazing landscapes and stunning coastlines. Life's better with a holiday booked!\r\n\r\nDiscover art and culture in Italy, hike the majestic Alps in Switzerland and Austria, meander quaint mountain villages or walking trails in France or fall in love with the alluring landscapes of Slovenia. Where will you step into Summer?\r\n\r\nOur self guided walks offer total flexibility, while our guided walks with local experts will reveal the hidden gems of your walking destination. Whether you’re travelling solo, or with family, we have walks for all levels, from easy strolls to challenging hikes. Whether you’re a seasoned hiker or casual walker, let us show you the beauty of our walking holidays.\r&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:897,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">Explore <a data-udi="umb://document/ab0ac9824ee54b89b9d14e05eff45356" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ab0ac9824ee54b89b9d14e05eff45356}" title="City Breaks">Italy's cities</a> like <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a> with its landmarks and <a data-udi="umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b}" title="Florence">Florence</a> with its art. Visit <a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona">Verona's</a> historic streets, take a <a data-udi="umb://document/7484af88886b4493a9304025f4744fc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7484af88886b4493a9304025f4744fc8}" title="Italy">family trip</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722}" title="Tuscany">Tuscany</a> or see <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice's</a> canals. Or, take a relaxing <a data-udi="umb://document/3848018580784607a13363dd2dd1885d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3848018580784607a13363dd2dd1885d}" title="Italy">Italy lake holiday</a> and visit the glamorous waters of <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda's</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a>, or <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a>, and <a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Iseo</a>.</span></p>
